rSERA - rails Search Engine Ranking Analyzer
---------

1. Overview

   rSERA is an Open Source tool for keeping up with 
   your position in search engine rankings. Dozens of 
   search engines are provided, and you can easily
   add or update the SEs in the database. Just add
   your own keyphrases and URLs and let rSERA do
   the job.
   
   rSERA is based on phpSera http://phpsera.sourceforge.net/

